summary:
My show is tomorrow
I can’t stop crying
The day I was looking forward to is actually the worst week ever
I have $500 in extra...
body:
My show is tomorrow

I can’t stop crying

The day I was looking forward to is actually the worst week ever

I have $500 in extra tickets I bought for my friends who now dont wanna go, I’m at a loss for $500 in tickets

I have to go pick my truck up from the mechanic for the second time this week, almost $1,000 total

My burns covering my chest are STILL ugly

And I was broken up with because he moved away a month ago, and now suddenly realized we can’t do long distance. Though I’d move there in 2 years.

@taylorswift this week is terrible
